jobInfo.postDescription:
岗位职责
1.Responsible for Emergency Call testing and error report							
2.Ability to create test cases according to user story							
3.Ability to understand test plan and test cases, to manage the test cases accurately	
4.Ability to perform the test cases with requested tools and systems					
5.Ability to understand testing flow and take accurate trace							
6.Ability to make error report and follow up the errors till the ticket is closed			
7.Ability to understand how to perform testing activities with test rack and vehicles	
8.Support Test environment (test rack and vehicle)setup	
任职要求	
1.University degree in Computer Science/ Electrical Engineering/ Telecommunications	
2.1 years+ experience in related filed , experience with testing in automotive industry	
3.Good knowledge in testing tools /systems, such like Jira, Canoe, etc would be plus	
4.Quick learner , good team work and good motivation							
Chinese & English (written and verbal) mandatory
jobInfo.address: 北京朝阳区霄云路33号大厦101

brandComInfo.introduce:
上海凌咚科技有限公司成立于2020年，创始人团队平均有15年以上的国内外汽车领域项目开发及管理经验。在共同的理念之下，依靠出色
的技术开发团队、先进的管理制度和迅捷的响应速度，公司致力于为客户提供高质量的技术支持和产品。在驾驶辅助ADAS & V2X（自主
移动能力），智能驾舱（空间组合能力），大数据（智能运算能力）等领域凭借特有的专业认知，为客户提供包括了原型设计、概念验证、
软件开发、专业测试及项目管理咨询等全方位解决方案。
凌咚科技希望与客户、员工共同成长。对外，追求为客户创造更多价值；对内，追求员工与公司的共同进步。未来，公司将坚持“不断创
新”、 “共同发展”的经营理念，为广大客户提供更加优质的服务和市场一流的产品。
